				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The kid is throwing a tantrum. Why does he have to wash all day? When are they going home? The mother explains that they will stay at the hostel for now, but in order to do so, they must participate in the chores. He shouldn’t run away again, losing him would mean losing everything."
